<p>2nd. Wednesday.<br/>Had lovely shave of 15 days growth &amp; sponge bath. how refreshing too, more than words can tell. Went with party of 100 to trenches, being in rear we lost touch with those ahead &amp; messed up so not knowing where we were to go or do I sent message to C.O. 17th. H.Qrs. &amp; rec'd reply at 11.30 to take party back to gully. The shell fire was awfull on support lines and caused much</p>
